events.name: ArtScience Late: Listening for the Dark
events.description:
ArtScience Late: Listening for the Dark
Thursday 19 January I 8:00pm
Lobby
Free admission
Presented by Venzha Christ, Director of ISSS (Indonesia Space Science Society) and the House of Natural Fiber (HONF) Foundation

Featuring: 
Yudianto Asmoro
Irene Agrivina
VJ NumberOne
DJ MetzDub- Dubyouth Soundsystem
Haryono 
Bayu Bawono

Join us for a compelling encounter with space, as Indonesian artist Venzha Christ uses his body as a transmitter to receive and decode signals from the planets and the stars. What will we hear?

This programme is part of the Art and Science of Space season
